OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain and drizzle at first.
OL,7,FThe rain and drizzle will turn more
OL,8,Fpersistent through the day, perhaps
OL,9,Fwith some heavier bursts over hills.
OL,10,FFeeling chilly.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRain moves away east. Then
OL,13,Fbroken cloud and clear spells
OL,14,Ffollowing, along with possible a few
OL,15,Flight showers, these most likely
OL,16,Facross western areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
