OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,6,Fisolated showers until mid to late
OL,7,Fafternoon, then the showers become
OL,8,Fmore widespread, frequent and often
OL,9,Fheavy, with a chance of thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FWindy
OL,12,Fat the start of the week with showers
OL,13,For longer spells of rain. However,
OL,14,Ftemperatures will also start to rise,
OL,15,Fwith more settled weather likely later
OL,16,Fin the week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
